oracle.ord.spark.streaming

Class OrdSparkFrameProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.ord.spark.streaming.OrdSparkFrameProcessor

  • public abstract class OrdSparkFrameProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
    OrdSparkFrameProcessor is an abstract class which allows processing video frames in a flat map function in Spark. Implementation must be threadsafe!
